'Tuan, telepon Anda berdering.'

00:20:32.040 --> 00:20:33.160 line:20%
'Mungkin, penerimaannya
lebih baik sekarang.

00:20:33.200 --> 00:20:35.720 line:20%
'Krishna, bisakah kamu fokus pada ban?
- Ya.'

00:20:37.280 --> 00:20:39.560 line:20%
'Hei, kamu mau air?'

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:44.760 line:20%
'Tidak, sayang..
- Baiklah, biarkan aku memompa, kamu bisa minum air.'

00:20:44.800 --> 00:20:45.680 line:20%
'Berikan aku bayinya.'

00:20:46.760 --> 00:20:48.560 line:20%
'Tidak sayang.  Jangan menangis.'

00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:54.120 line:20%
'Bayimu sangat lucu.'